      6th May 2011: Image Warehouse 0.94 released

    %p
      The next release of Image Warehouse is out.

    %p
      Primarily a bug fix release, it includes these fixes:

    %p
      %ul
        %li
          %b iwhd no longer segfaults during garbage-collection
          %br
          [bug introduced in 0.91]
          %br
          %br

        %li
          %b iwhd now emits syntactically valid JSON output for the root query
          %br
          Before, it omitted the "providers": tag before the list of provider
          descriptions.
          %br
          [bug introduced in the beginning]

